            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>I fratelli <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Angelus"
                                >Angelo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs> e <persName><name ref="Baro"
                                >Barone</name></persName>, figli del <persName>fu <name ref="Carbo"
                                >Carbone</name></persName>, donano a <persName><name ref="Donnulina"
                                >Donnolina</name></persName> figlia del <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notaio</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                        >Ildebrando</name></persName>, 2 appezzamenti di terra, que sunt campora,
                        posti in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/166"
                        >Tempagnano</placeName>: il primo, posto ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/166">a Potio Lopi</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> unum capo con terra
                        della <rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Churches">San Pantaleone</orgName>,
                        aliud caput con terra di <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Wido">Wittone</name></persName>, barbano dei suddetti fratelli,
                        latus unum in via publica, aliud latus con terra di <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Bonus"
                            >Bono</name></persName> e con terra del <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monastero</rs> di <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/71">San Ponziano</orgName>; il secondo, posto
                        ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/166">a le Muriccia</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> uno capo con terra
                        del suddetto Bono, aliud caput con terra della <rs key="#Churches"
                            >chiesa</rs> di <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Churches"
                            >San Martino</orgName>, latus unum con terra di <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Rodelandus"
                                >Rodilando</name></persName>, aliud latus con terra del suddetto
                        Wittone, per una misura complessiva di un moggio con tutte le loro
                        dipendenze, ricevendo <rs key="#Meritum/launechild #Jewels">launechild
                            meritum anulum unum aureum</rs> da <persName key="#Witness #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodolfo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs> del <persName>fu <name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildebrando</name></persName>. Chiedono al <rs
                            key="#Writer #Other_palatine_officer #Notary">notaio del sacro
                            palazzo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Other_palatine_officer #Notary"><name ref="Paulus"
                                >Paolo</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                        sottoscrittori: Rodolfo notarius dom. imp., <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rusticus">Rustico</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Gherardus">Gherardo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Baro">Barone</name></persName> del <persName
                            key="#Notary">fu <name ref="Pepo">Pepo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Azo"
                                >Azzo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gherardo</name></persName>. <rs key="#Copyist">Copiatore</rs>:
                            <persName key="#Copyist #Notary"><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ugo</name></persName><rs key="#Notary"> notarius dom. reg.</rs></ab>
                        </div>
